project_descr:
Sector plan for Phase-out of HCFCs in the Solvent Sector in China (Stage-II, for  
2020 and 2025 compliance)

outputs.output_descr:
Phaseout target in the Stage II HPMP in the Solvent Sector Plan is developed and classified into four stages, i.e.
20% reduction of the baseline consumption by 2018, 35% reduction by 2020, 70% reduction by 2023 and
100% reduction by 2026.
